tember)\n\nAccording to King Saud, King Hussain of Jordan desires to conclude a military agreement with Saudi Arabia similar to that recently concluded between Jordan and Syria. This agreement is believed to involve a joint military command and a joint operations staff under the authority of the Arab joint command in Cairo. Jordan's move toward co-operation with Saudi Arabia may be part of the price of major Egyptian-Syrian-Saudi arms aid for Jordan's National Guard. King Saud has invited military representatives of Egypt, Iraq, Syria and Lebanon to meet in Riyadh on 7 September to discuss measures to improve defense of the Jordan-Israel border", "token_count": 111, "token_end_0based": 110, "token_start_0based": 0, "token_text": "the arab-israeli situation information as of 1700 6 september according to king saud king hussain of jordan desires to conclude a military agreement with saudi arabia similar to that recently concluded between jordan and syria this agreement is believed to involve a joint military command and a joint operations staff under the authority of the arab joint command in cairo jordan's move toward co-operation with saudi arabia may be part of the price of major egyptian-syrian-saudi arms aid for jordan's national guard king saud has invited military representatives of egypt iraq syria and lebanon to meet in riyadh on 7 september to discuss measures to improve defense of the jordan-israel border", "unred_source_page": 12}
